04:42.519 --> 04:43.986
"Everyone Must Get Laid."

04:44.054 --> 04:46.521
So, what can I do? I-I want to help.

04:46.523 --> 04:47.722
With the sex dance?

04:47.791 --> 04:48.857
Or the school mystery?

04:48.925 --> 04:50.192
The... second thing.

04:50.260 --> 04:52.861
