They just want to put slop on plates.

14:14.891 --> 14:17.492
- Won't you help them, Steve?
- I will.

14:17.556 --> 14:20.162
Your whack on the head
knocked some sense into me.

14:20.230 --> 14:22.430
We've got to get this
evidence to Turlington.

14:23.284 --> 14:25.033
I'll drive.

14:25.101 --> 14:27.569
Where does one buy a
telescoping driving cane?

14:27.637 --> 14:28.903
- Eddie Bauer.
- Oh.

14:33.258 --> 14:34.843
Do you think it was suicide?

14:34.911 --> 14:36.444
At least we have the recording.

14:36.513 --> 14:38.046
We can still take it to the cops.

14:38.114 --> 14:41.183
We should close his eyes.

14:41.251 --> 14:42.316
Oh, shit.

14:42.386 --> 14:44.853
This freak doesn't have any eyelids.

14:45.616 --> 14:46.755
Gather round.

14:46.768 --> 14:48.990
All you cops are gonna
want to hear this.

14:49.059 --> 14:51.259
Yeah, so put down
your doughnuts, piggies,

14:51.327 --> 14:52.360
and listen up!

14:58.268 --> 14:59.934
It's so dang hot under this.

15:00.003 --> 15:01.335
I'm dying.

15:01.337 --> 15:04.539
Why did I guzzle that Arizona Iced Tea?

15:06.009 --> 15:09.544
Steve's wearing a jacket
and a long-sleeve tee?

15:09.613 --> 15:11.079
What is wrong with him?

15:12.350 --> 15:14.082
Well, we have nothing.

15:14.150 --> 15:15.617
Wait, don't turn it off.

15:15.685 --> 15:18.086
I'm about to sing a song from "Wicked."

15:18.154 --> 15:20.021
The wizard is ready for you.

15:27.631 --> 15:29.631
Turlington's dead,
the whole town's about

15:29.699 --> 15:30.765
to get poisoned...

15:31.686 --> 15:34.969
And now Lewis wants to take
me up to the tree farm.

15:34.971 --> 15:36.704
Oh, God! He's gonna kill me!

15:36.773 --> 15:38.973
No. He's gonna kill us.

15:38.975 --> 15:40.374
You're not coming.

15:40.376 --> 15:43.377
It's sweet of you to worry about me,
but I'm coming.

15:43.379 --> 15:45.046
Fine. But to be clear,

15:45.115 --> 15:46.514
I wasn't trying to keep you safe.

15:46.583 --> 15:48.450
I just didn't want to be around you.

15:48.518 --> 15:50.452
Your little bowl bothers me.

15:50.520 --> 15:52.320
All the scooting and scraping.

15:52.388 --> 15:54.656
It's... very unpleasant.

15:54.724 --> 15:56.796
_

15:58.528 --> 16:00.262
I thought it was about time you all saw

16:00.330 --> 16:01.463
where the magic happens.

16:01.531 --> 16:03.131
I call it magic because I don't know

16:03.199 --> 16:05.133
what any of these machines do.

16:05.201 --> 16:09.203
I have a bunch of fat guys who
make the machines eat the trees.

16:09.205 --> 16:10.672
They're so fat.

16:10.740 --> 16:12.140
You should see their work pants.

16:12.208 --> 16:14.276
The size! When they hang them up to dry,

16:14.344 --> 16:16.278
they look like medieval tapestries!

16:16.346 --> 16:18.814
Some of them are truly gorgeous.

16:19.816 --> 16:22.484
I'm gonna sneak off and do some recon.

16:22.552 --> 16:24.486
Klaus, it's super-dangerous.

16:24.554 --> 16:28.290
Don't worry.
Ol' Klaus can take care of himself.

16:28.358 --> 16:30.292
♪ Bum-bum-bum-bum bum-bum-bum-bum ♪

16:30.360 --> 16:31.159
Shh!

16:31.227 --> 16:33.962
♪ Bwaaaaa bwaaa! ♪

16:34.030 --> 16:36.965
♪ Bwaaaa, bwah-bwah! ♪

16:37.033 --> 16:38.767
Oop! I've been caught immediately!

16:38.835 --> 16:40.101
No! Not the toilet!

16:46.376 --> 16:47.709
This isn't funny anymore.

16:47.778 --> 16:50.712
We gotta do something about
these Catatonic Cathys.

16:50.781 --> 16:52.381
It's been days.

16:53.383 --> 16:54.516
Okay, that was a little funny.

16:55.335 --> 16:57.452
Don't worry, Mom. I called in some help.

16:57.521 --> 16:59.654
Dr. Ray?

16:59.723 --> 17:01.323
I-I thought you died.

17:01.391 --> 17:03.257
- No.
- Oh, okay.

17:03.259 --> 17:05.327
Let's see what we've got here.

17:05.395 --> 17:06.404
Mm-hmm.

17:06.462 --> 17:07.929
With extreme cases like this,

17:07.998 --> 17:11.598
I find that returning to the
scene of the initial event

17:11.667 --> 17:15.002
sometimes helps snap
the patient out of it.

17:16.209 --> 17:17.672
How long could this take?

17:17.674 --> 17:19.674
I don't know. I gave up 30 minutes ago.

17:19.742 --> 17:21.474
Ooh! A Cinnabon!

17:21.477 --> 17:23.645
I have one last idea.

17:30.420 --> 17:32.354
♪ Come, my lady, come, come, my lady ♪

17:32.422 --> 17:33.821
♪ You're my butterfly, sugar, baby ♪

17:33.890 --> 17:36.758
♪ Come, my lady, come, come, my lady ♪

17:36.826 --> 17:38.893
♪ You're my butterfly, sugar, baby ♪

17:38.962 --> 17:40.562
♪ Such a sexy, sexy,
pretty little thing ♪

17:40.630 --> 17:42.096
♪ Fierce nipple pierce

17:42.098 --> 17:43.965
♪ You got me sprung
with your tongue ring ♪

17:44.034 --> 17:46.234
♪ And I ain't gonna lie
'cause your living gets me high ♪

17:46.302 --> 17:47.435
♪ So to keep you by my side

17:47.504 --> 17:48.970
♪ There's nothing that I won't try ♪

17:49.039 --> 17:50.972
♪ Butterflies in her
eyes and looks to kill ♪

17:51.041 --> 17:53.441
♪ Time is passing I'm asking
"Could this be real?" ♪

17:53.510 --> 17:55.177
♪ 'Cause I can't sleep,
I can't hold still ♪

17:55.245 --> 17:57.645
♪ The only thing I really
know is she got sex appeal ♪

17:57.714 --> 17:59.514
♪ I can feel, too much is never enough ♪

17:59.546 --> 18:02.050
Well, I'm out of ideas.

18:02.118 --> 18:03.385
Give it up, you guys!

18:03.453 --> 18:05.587
They're gonna be vegetables forever!

18:13.864 --> 18:15.129
Oh, hey, fun.

18:15.199 --> 18:16.931
The whole family's mall walking.

18:16.933 --> 18:20.068
What do you think?
Could old Al use a few laps?

18:21.405 --> 18:23.471
Do you even hear yourself?
"Oh, hey, fun.

18:23.540 --> 18:24.606
"The whole family's mall walking.

18:24.674 --> 18:26.608
Yeah." Oh, you're the town fool.

18:26.676 --> 18:28.676
Just get of here with your dignity.

18:28.745 --> 18:30.945
Smell ya on the flip side, skater bois.

18:30.947 --> 18:33.147
What the hell was that?

18:35.219 --> 18:37.151
Huh? Huh?

18:37.153 --> 18:39.221
Ha. Those are funny.

18:39.289 --> 18:40.889
They're not supposed to be funny.

18:40.957 --> 18:42.757
I think they're incredibly moving.

18:42.759 --> 18:46.828
And now for the main event...
making the whole town puke.

18:46.897 --> 18:49.431
With this gross stuff
I found in my trunk.

18:50.593 --> 18:51.499
Ugh!

18:51.568 --> 18:55.570
This pipe leads directly
to the town's water supply.

18:56.476 --> 18:57.906
You think that's bad?

18:57.974 --> 18:59.641
Get ready to gasp again.

18:59.709 --> 19:01.910
There's a mole among our ranks.

19:04.248 --> 19:05.980
This is Turlington's phone,

19:06.049 --> 19:10.518
and this is the contact labeled
"hall monitor spy."

19:13.523 --> 19:15.189
We could have made a great team, Smith.

19:15.259 --> 19:17.992
But instead, you chose to be
murdered by your classmates.

19:18.061 --> 19:19.261
Get him!

19:20.931 --> 19:22.931
You almost thought
of everything, Lewis.

19:22.999 --> 19:26.334
But there's one thing you
forgot to have thought of...

19:26.402 --> 19:30.204
In juvie, I only worked out my legs!

19:34.945 --> 19:36.047
Ooh!

19:39.549 --> 19:41.549
Lewis, you've poisoned
your last person...

19:43.920 --> 19:44.953
...me.

19:46.022 --> 19:48.222
Hold it right there!

19:48.292 --> 19:50.358
Hey! I thought we flushed you!

19:50.426 --> 19:54.296
When you flush,
you've gotta check the bowl.

19:54.364 --> 19:56.765
Lunch ladies, attack!

19:57.968 --> 20:00.168
Oh!

20:05.075 --> 20:06.110
Ooh!

20:11.247 --> 20:13.047
Aah!

20:13.687 --> 20:15.384
Aaah!

20:16.987 --> 20:19.453
Aaah!

20:23.527 --> 20:25.760
Wh-Wh-What happened?

20:25.762 --> 20:26.795
Easy, bud.

20:26.863 --> 20:29.463
You're home safe in
the school cafeteria.

20:29.465 --> 20:31.265
Wh-What's going in my arm?

20:31.267 --> 20:32.800
You lost a lot of fluids,

20:32.869 --> 20:35.403
so Agnes put you on a Salisbury IV.

20:35.472 --> 20:38.606
Look, the brown's returning
to your cheeks already.

20:38.675 --> 20:42.276
Thanks for saving me from Lewis,
and from myself.

20:42.346 --> 20:44.078
Hey, what happened to Lewis?

20:44.148 --> 20:45.613
He got away basically.

20:45.682 --> 20:47.749
Lewis gets away again!

20:47.818 --> 20:50.218
Hey, you wanna buy a mattress factory?

20:50.286 --> 20:53.155
[BLEEP] yeah, I do!

20:54.791 --> 20:58.893
- Billy?
